quote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/26/203109_26cda7fe635baaeb0b574c2d51241af7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F26%2F203109_26cda7fe635baaeb0b574c2d51241af7.jpg&h=9ac4a10d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男朋友收工煮飯佢食<br />\n佢竟然話我最鍾意食既雜菜飯似狗糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n擺上黎俾大家評下理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n似：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔似：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我建議你落一小舊牛油落去，溶左撈飯食</blockquote><br />\n前題：啲豆放入飯煲前有冇溶雪同飛水？<br />\n冇的話真係難食過狗飯</blockquote><br />\n好撚肯定剪開個袋就倒入飯煲祝樓主男友身體健康<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q4xa7T.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ4xa7T.gif&h=20a245c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3686a9c97f8524f29e509013975cd613cb02f991","tid":55490,"uid":8264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T16:48:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f867e84354d44d5175e6dd0999e00538c038dfc","tid":55490,"uid":56878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T16:54:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係十五妹？</blockquote><br />\n無心心<br />\n唔似"},{"pid":"f2c3968fe70c15962bd8e4d8af6c2e64e77e55dd","tid":55490,"uid":66844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T17:01:20.000Z","msg":"其實你都幾懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a993a4df98bc57df68dc3d3ae11005102d198a","tid":55490,"uid":26976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T17:06:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢種女仔娶得過<br />\n煮咁大兜狗飯似係要派俾流浪狗<br />\n有愛心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仆街虐畜